Package battleship

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Battleship
    This class extends Ship and describes a ship of length 4
    BattleshipGame
    This is the main class, containing the main method for playing the game.
    Cruiser
    This class extends Ship and describes a ship of length 3
    Destroyer
    This class extends Ship and describes a ship of length 2
    EmptySea
    This class extends Ship and describes a part of the ocean that doesn't have a ship in it.
    Ocean
    Contains a 10*10 array of Ships, representing an "ocean" and some methods to manipulate it.
    OceanTest
    JUnit test class for Ocean.
    Ship
    Abstract class describing the characteristics common to all ships.
    ShipTest_v2
    JUnit test class for Ship.
    Submarine
    This class extends Ship and describes a ship of length 1
